{"tha-ap236:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap236:0.2":"Udakasanavagga ","tha-ap236:0.3":"Kilanjadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap236:1.1":"“Tivarayam pure ramme, ","tha-ap236:1.2":"nalakaro aham tada; ","tha-ap236:1.3":"Siddhatthe lokapajjote, ","tha-ap236:1.4":"pasanna janata tahim. ","tha-ap236:2.1":"Pujattham lokanathassa, ","tha-ap236:2.2":"kilanjam pariyesati; ","tha-ap236:2.3":"Buddhapujam karontanam, ","tha-ap236:2.4":"kilanjam adadim aham. ","tha-ap236:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap236:3.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap236:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap236:3.4":"kilanjassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap236:4.1":"Sattasattatikappamhi, ","tha-ap236:4.2":"raja asim jaladdharo; ","tha-ap236:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap236:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap236:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap236:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap236:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap236:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kilanjadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap236:7.1":"Kilanjadayakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}